membership:
The Better Regulation Watchdog Network is a coalition 66 civil society organisations, 7 of which are represented in the steering group. Many of the member organisations are federations or umbrella organisations themselves, representing a wide range of organisations from Europe and beyond.&#xd;
A full list of member organisations is available here:&#xd;
http://betterregwatch.eu/BRWN_members.pdf

